<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>재고 알림</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-box.danger {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border-left-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .part-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .site-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .stock-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .stock-current {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .stock-status {
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .status-in-stock {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .status-low-stock {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .status-out-of-stock {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>재고 알림</h1>
        <p>모니터링 대상 부품의 재고 상태가 변경되었습니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="alert-box {{#if (eq stockStatus 'out_of_stock')}}danger{{else if (eq stockStatus 'low_stock')}}warning{{/if}}">
        <div class="part-number">{{product.partNumber}}</div>
        <p>{{product.manufacturer}} - {{product.description}}</p>
        
        <div class="site-info">
            <h3>{{site}} 사이트</h3>
            <div class="stock-info">
                <div>
                    <div>현재 재고</div>
                    <div class="stock-current">{{formatNumber stockQuantity}}개</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stock-status status-{{stockStatus}}">
                    {{stockStatusText}}
                </div>
            </div>
            <p><strong>납기일:</strong> {{leadTime}}</p>
        </div>

        {{#if productUrl}}
        <a href="{{productUrl}}" class="cta-button">제품 상세페이지 보기</a>
        {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>이 메일은 자동으로 발송됩니다. 문의사항은 관리자에게 연락해 주세요.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
